    MIGHTY MOUSE NEVER GOT OLDER
</div><br>
<br>
    We all know exercise makes you healthy but it’s hard to understand the true effect it has on the body.  Imagine achieving the benefits of wisdom through experience while having the physical attributes we did when we were younger.  Being young is easy, staying young, however, is much more difficult.  People have been searching for the elusive fountain of youth since the beginning of time.  We are bombarded with suggestive advertising steering us towards magic formulas, pills, diets, etc. with promise to make you look and feel younger.  These often pricey, quick fix products try to convince the consumer there is a short cut to achieving physical youth but in the end, they cannot deliver on their promises.
    <br /><br />
    <table align="right">
